1
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:11,760
Xiao Bai.

2
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:13,160
How dare you!

3
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:14,600
How dare you kidnap the execution ground!

4
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:16,080
Guards, arrest him.

5
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:17,520
