6
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:23,000
I am the Crown Prince. Here is the imperial edict.

7
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,039
Are you okay?

8
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,400
You are the Crown Prince.

9
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:46,960
I've found out your identity.

10
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:51,680
She is General Wu Yi, commander of Taizhou.

11
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:53,759
This is her military badge.

12
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:58,000
My benefactor is such a great character.

13
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:03,040
Lord Yan, look carefully.

14
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:04,320
General recruited soldiers.

15
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:05,800
What's wrong with that?

16
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,040
Just now,

17
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:08,160
I didn't see it clearly.

18
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,400
The Crown Prince is here.

19
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,560
He is right.

20
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:14,240
General Xu is innocent.

21
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:15,160
Not guilty.

22
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,760
I'm innocent.

23
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,440
Great, she's fine.

24
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:22,240
Sanniang is wronged.

25
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,040
Let's go.

26
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,240
Great!

27
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:25,120
Great.

28
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:27,040
So...

29
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:29,240
So I hid my identity as the crown prince.

30
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:33,840
But I will help you find your memories.

31
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:35,120
I will.

32
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:38,440
Can I not call you Xiao Bai now?

33
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:40,640
I should call you Young Master Ban.

34
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:41,240
No, no, no.

35
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,920
I'm not your son.

36
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,680
You're just my aunt.

37
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,440
Here comes the imperial edict.

38
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:07,160
I accept the decree.

39
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:11,720
By God's will,

40
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:13,800
According to the imperial edict,

41
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:17,720
the Commander of Taizhou Guards to suppress General Wu Yi.

42
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:18,960
Xu Qianzhen.

43
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,200
Since you've lost your memory,

44
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,840
I feel sorry for him.

45
00:03:21,920 --> 00:03:24,720
So I'll lead the Commander of Gusu

46
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:27,160
to assist the governor of Yan Wei to fight against the war.

47
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:30,200
We'll call him back when he regains his memory.

48
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,120
and send another Taizhou guards

49
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,640
and reinforcements.

50
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,160
Respect this.

51
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,200
Yes, Your Majesty.

52
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:45,120
I shall take my leave.

53
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:55,760
I misunderstood you before.

54
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:56,880
and offended you.

55
00:03:56,960 --> 00:04:00,320
I’m counting on you to fight against the Japanese.

56
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,200
It’s my pleasure.

57
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:04,080
I will do my best.

58
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,960
1,900 pence.

59
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:09,720
2,100 pence.

60
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,600
Done.

61
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:14,920
Gosh.

62
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:16,800
It's such a tough time.

63
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:20,200
It's not easy for you and Xiao Bai.

64
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:22,200
I can finally relax.

65
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,960
After going through so much,

66
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,760
I'm sure I like him too.

67
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,400
He likes me too.

68
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:32,159
That's great.

69
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:35,840
When can I meet my Mr. Right?

70
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:38,120
You are so nice.

71
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:40,680
God will definitely give you

72
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:42,760
a tall and handsome man.

73
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:45,800
I don't like toy boys.

74
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:57,960
How have you been?

75
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,600
You know me?

76
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,400
Look at my cutting skills.

77
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:05,200
you'll know who I am.

78
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:07,440
How arrogant.

79
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:15,280
Do you remember when you were 15,

80
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:16,720
when we were 15?

81
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:17,840
[The fact that we met.]

82
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:18,920
Who are you?

83
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:19,960
Don't try to get close to me.

84
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:26,280
General Xu.

85
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,320
We'll meet again soon.

86
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,840
What? I haven't had enough.

87
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,159
The Crown Prince's calligraphy.

88
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:49,040
The Crown Prince's calligraphy?

89
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,720
His Highness's calligraphy.

90
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:53,000
Your favorite tofu.

91
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:55,440
The tofu is so fresh

92
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:55,960
Try it.

93
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:56,440
It's free.

94
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,600
The Crown Prince's calligraphy.

95
00:05:58,920 --> 00:05:59,840
Your Highness.

96
