Today is a good day.

98
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:05,760
I'll give you a piece of meat.

99
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:06,760
Take a piece of meat.

100
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:08,800
Ma'am.

101
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:12,120
General and the Crown Prince are a perfect match.

102
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:13,840
Especially the Crown Prince.

103
